Test certificate for use in dev thanks to SO:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10175812/how-to-create-a-self-signed-certificate-with-openssl
and
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/808669/convert-a-cert-pem-certificate-to-a-pfx-certificate


#1: generate a self signed cert:
openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem -days 365

#2: combine into one pfx for kestrel:
openssl pkcs12 -inkey key.pem -in cert.pem -export -out testcert.pfx

#3: cleanup
rm *.pem
